WEBVTT

00:03:58.169 --> 00:04:00.638
We take the kids to Australia.

00:04:00.638 --> 00:04:03.350
And then more years pass,

00:04:03.350 --> 00:04:05.740
and the cancer begins to grow.

00:04:05.740 --> 00:04:08.275
This time, there's new treatments on the horizon.

00:04:08.275 --> 00:04:10.211
They're exotic. They're experimental.

00:04:10.211 --> 00:04:13.419
They're going to attack the cancer in new ways.

00:04:13.419 --> 00:04:17.745
So he enters a clinical trial, and it works.

00:04:17.745 --> 00:04:19.674
The cancer begins to shrink,

00:04:19.674 --> 00:04:21.951
and for the third time,

00:04:21.951 --> 00:04:25.310
we've dodged death.

00:04:25.310 --> 00:04:28.607
So now I ask you,

00:04:28.607 --> 00:04:30.996
how do I feel